意外爆紅，從此被網友暱稱「ガチムチ兄貴（肌肉大哥）」、「ビリー兄貴」，隨後更親訪日本參加活動，還親切對女粉絲「公主抱」，吸引全場觀眾拿手機拍下珍貴時刻。<br />\n<br />\n生前人緣甚佳的比利海靈頓車禍過世，朋友陸續發文悼念，他的母親為了讓全球粉絲知情，公開發文「我現在心情非常沉痛悲傷，希望大家知道我的兒子過世了，我愛你兒子。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1123212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1123212&d=r4H9ykDQE6JaJs7ebpxHnywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=6f266a87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1123212</a><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895c039d6b1536a4d40cebd2db4e2390dca54ebd","tid":579553,"uid":42947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:39:12.000Z","msg":"一代妖精殞落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1092763c8fe7ff959fc60ef0e829a07da9e023","tid":579553,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:40:23.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3063880b872995b7f38f882ae138418d06ec19b8","tid":579553,"uid":5044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:40:53.000Z","msg":"Gachi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f4eb1e706c763ff62715a3f0adf33cb6c076f3","tid":579553,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3167dd0331d3919695845694e87bc056946b8ac0","tid":579553,"uid":5044,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T18:39:00.000Z","msg":"美國男星比利海靈頓（Billy Herrington）在美國時間2日因車禍意外身亡，享年48歲。他生前拍同志A片為人熟知，並擁有「森之妖精」的封號，也被日本網友稱為「兄貴系」男優，擁有健壯胸肌，母親也發文「我愛你兒子」悼念，震驚大批粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n比利海靈頓身高185公分，體重高達111公斤，健壯身材因為被當時交往的女友公開裸照，意外因此成名，隨後入行拍攝同志片，一段從森林走出來的經典畫面，被稱為「森之妖精